0405|accessdate=2015-06-24|newspaper=[[中國時報|中國時報]]|date=2014-06-26|archive-date=2020-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506225410/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140626004752-260405|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

